{"post_stream":{"posts":[{"id":3241159,"name":"","username":"oman19","avatar_template":"/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/o/f19dbf/{size}.png","created_at":"2023-10-15T19:56:59.022Z","cooked":"<p>Hey guys, my team’s current robot code still uses JoystickButton, but I heard that it’s getting removed soon and we should use CommandXboxController instead. How can I do that? I was reading through the documentations and I am very confused. I am pretty much an absolute beginner atm. Can someone please help me? For example, how should I replace this code?<br>
